aly|pandemic of COVID-19 in Italy]].<ref name=\"12 March update\"/>}}\n|time       =\n|team1      = [[Juventus F.C.|Juventus]] {{fbaicon|ITA}}\n|score      =\n|team2      = {{fbaicon|FRA}} [[Olympique Lyonnais|Lyon]]\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Juventus Stadium]], [[Turin]]\n|attendance =\n|referee    =\n|report     = https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2020/matches/round=2001141/match=2027133/index.html\n}}\n----\n{{Football box\n|id         = Tottenham Hotspur v RB Leipzig\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|2|19|df=y}}\n|time       = 21:00 {{small|(20:00 [[Greenwich Mean Time|GMT]])}}\n|team1      = [[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]] {{fbaicon|ENG}}\n|score      = 0\u20131\n|team2      = {{fbaicon|GER}} [[RB Leipzig]]\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     =\n*[[Timo Werner|Werner]] {{goal|58|pen.}}\n|stadium    = [[Tottenham Hotspur Stadium]], [[London]]\n|attendance = 60,095<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/newsfiles/ucl/2020/2027122_fr.pdf |title=Full Time Summary Round of 16 1st Leg \u2013 Tottenham Hotspur v RB Leipzig |work=UEFA.com |publisher=Union of European Football Associations |date=19 February 2020 |accessdate=19 February 2020}}</ref>\n|referee    = [[C\u00fcneyt \u00c7ak\u0131r]] ([[Turkish Football Federation|Turkey]])\n|report     = https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/season=2020/matches/round=2001141/match=2027122/index.html\n}}\n{{Football box\n|id         = RB Leipzig v Tottenham Hotspur\n|date       = {{Start date|2020|3|10|df=y}}\n|time       = 21:00\n|team1      = [[RB Leipzig]] {{fbaicon|GER}}\n|score      = 3\u20130\n|team2      = {{fbaicon|ENG}} [[Tottenham Hotspur F.C.|Tottenham Hotspur]]\n|goals1     =\n*[[Marcel Sabitzer|Sabitzer]] {{goal|10||21}}\n*[[Emil Forsberg|Forsberg]] {{goal|87}}\n|goals2     =\n|stadium    = [[Red Bull Arena (Leipzig)|Red Bull Arena]], [[Leipzig]]\n|attendance = 42,146<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/newsfiles/ucl/2020/2027128_fr.pdf |title=Full Time Summary Rou