 to the [[2020 coronavirus pandemic in Europe]].<ref name=\"week postponed\"/><ref name=\"QF_SF_F_draw\">{{cite web |url=https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/draws/2020/2001142/ |title=UEFA Champions League quarter-final, semi-final and final draws |publisher=UEFA.com |quote=due to the spread of COVID-19 in Europe and related decisions made by different governments, all UEFA club competitions matches scheduled this week are postponed  |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200408084832/https://www.uefa.com/insideuefa/news/newsid=2641054.html |archivedate=8 April 2020 |date=15 March 2020 |url-status=live}}</ref><!--<section end=QF />\n\n===Summary===\n<section begin=QF />\nThe first legs will be played on , and the second legs will be played on  2020.-->\n\n'''Qualified teams'''\n{{Columns-start|num=2}}\n*{{fbaicon|FRA}} [[Paris Saint-Germain F.C.|Paris Saint-Germain]]\n*{{fbaicon|GER}} [[RB Leipzig]]\n{{Column}}\n*{{fbaicon|ITA}} [[Atalanta B.C.|Atalanta]]\n*{{fbaicon|ESP}} [[Atl\u00e9tico Madrid]]\n{{Columns-end}}<!--{{TwoLegStart}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||1|||[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|7/8 Apr}}]]|[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|14/15 Apr}}]]}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||2|||[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|7/8 Apr}}]]|[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|14/15 Apr}}]]}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||3|||[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|7/8 Apr}}]]|[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|14/15 Apr}}]]}}\n{{TwoLegResult|||4|||[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|7/8 Apr}}]]|[[2019\u201320 UEFA Champions League knockout phase#Matches 2|{{small|14/15 Apr}}]]}}\n|}--><section end=QF /><!--\n\n===Matches===\n{{Football box\n|id         =\n|date       = 7/8 {{Start date|2020|4||df=y}}\n|time       = 21:00\n|team1      = {{fbaicon|}}\n|score   